  "title": "Cook and Cleaner",
  "description": "<p>Preschool Chef / Childcare Cook (Weekday Day Shift) <br /><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Plan and prepare healthy meals, snacks, and beverages for children in line with HMCCP guidelines</p></li><li><p>Ensure food is served in a clean, safe, and inviting environment.</p></li><li><p>Maintain high hygiene standards during food preparation, handling, and serving.</p></li><li><p>Ensure meals are sufficient in quantity, with portions available for additional servings if needed.</p></li><li><p>Keep the kitchen clean and organized by following a daily, weekly, and monthly maintenance checklist.</p></li><li><p>Manage grocery and kitchen equipment purchases with the approval of the Head of School.</p></li><li><p>Assist in maintaining cleanliness and hygiene in designated areas of the school, ensuring a safe and sanitary environment for children and staff. ( e.g. classrooms, corridors..etc)</p></li><li><p>Support the smooth operation of the centre by assisting with other duties as required by campus leadership.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Certification: <strong>WSQ Basic Food Hygiene Certificate (required)</strong></p></li><li><p>Experience: Prior experience in childcare centres or hospitality (e.g. hotel/restaurant kitchens) is highly preferred</p></li></ul><p><strong>Skills:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Knowledge of child nutrition and food safety</p></li><li><p>Ability to cook efficiently for large groups</p></li><li><p>Strong sense of cleanliness, responsibility, and organization<strong>  </strong><br /><strong> </strong></p><p>If you are interested, please click here to apply :  <a href=\"https://job-boards.greenhouse.io/gge-asia/jobs/7566240\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job Application for GGE SG - Chef at Guidepost Global Education Asia</a></p></li></ul><p><strong>Who We Are:</strong></p><p>Guidepost Global Education (GGE) is one of the largest operators of Montessori schools in Asia, dedicated to transforming education to better serve families everywhere – children and parents. GGE offers programs for children ages 0-12 through an extensive network of 27 campuses spanning Hong Kong, Singapore, Bali, and key cities in Mainland China. GGE currently operates schools under the Guidepost & Nest Preschool brands. <br /></p><p>For information about Guidepost Global Education, please visit:  https://guideposteducation.com/</p><p>or https://nestpreschool.sg/</p>",
